WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.875
Israelis are

00:00:00.875 --> 00:00:01.751
on the streets

00:00:01.751 --> 00:00:03.336
protesting, demanding

00:00:03.336 --> 00:00:04.921
a cease fire agreement

00:00:04.921 --> 00:00:06.131
after defense officials

00:00:06.131 --> 00:00:08.383
said they recovered the bodies of six

00:00:08.383 --> 00:00:11.469
Israeli hostages murdered by Hamas,

00:00:11.678 --> 00:00:13.763
including Israeli-American Hirsh

00:00:13.763 --> 00:00:16.850
Goldberg, Poland, who was 23 years old.

00:00:17.225 --> 00:00:18.518
An IDF spokesman said

00:00:18.518 --> 00:00:21.187
Hamas brutally killed the six

00:00:21.187 --> 00:00:22.188
young adults

00:00:22.188 --> 00:00:23.356
in an underground tunnel

00:00:23.356 --> 00:00:24.315
near Rafah,

00:00:24.315 --> 00:00:25.525
a short time before

00:00:25.525 --> 00:00:27.152
Israeli forces arrived.

00:00:27.152 --> 00:00:29.029
Three of them would have been released

00:00:29.029 --> 00:00:30.613
in the early stages

00:00:30.613 --> 00:00:31.865
of a ceasefire agreement,

00:00:31.865 --> 00:00:34.659
two Israeli officials told CNN.

00:00:34.659 --> 00:00:35.201
An agreement,

00:00:35.201 --> 00:00:36.703
President Biden said last night

00:00:36.703 --> 00:00:38.496
was on the verge of happening,

00:00:38.496 --> 00:00:38.955
while Vice

00:00:38.955 --> 00:00:40.707
President Harris released a statement

00:00:40.707 --> 00:00:42.000
that reads, in part,

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:43.460
the threat Hamas poses

00:00:43.460 --> 00:00:45.045
to the people of Israel

00:00:45.045 --> 00:00:47.380
and American citizens in Israel

00:00:47.380 --> 00:00:48.631
must be eliminated

00:00:48.631 --> 00:00:51.426
and Hamas cannot control Gaza.

00:00:51.426 --> 00:00:53.803
The Palestinian people, too,

00:00:53.803 --> 00:00:55.180
have suffered under Hamas

00:00:55.180 --> 00:00:56.890
rule for nearly two decades.

00:00:58.349 --> 00:00:58.850
Here with me

00:00:58.850 --> 00:01:00.435
now is IDF spokesman

00:01:00.435 --> 00:01:02.604
Lieutenant Colonel Nadav Shoshana.

00:01:02.604 --> 00:01:04.105
Thank you so much for being here.

00:01:04.105 --> 00:01:07.108
We are so incredibly devastated.

00:01:07.484 --> 00:01:09.611
for for Israel,

00:01:09.611 --> 00:01:12.614
for all of the families.

00:01:13.198 --> 00:01:15.658
it's just hard to even imagine

00:01:15.658 --> 00:01:17.702
how much pain everybody is in.

00:01:17.702 --> 00:01:20.163
And as a spokesperson for the IDF,

00:01:20.163 --> 00:01:22.123
I'd like for you to explain

00:01:22.123 --> 00:01:24.042
exactly what happened

00:01:24.042 --> 00:01:27.045
when these six bodies

00:01:27.045 --> 00:01:30.048
were found.

00:01:30.924 --> 00:01:31.883
Thank you.

00:01:31.883 --> 00:01:32.967
Thank you for having me.

00:01:32.967 --> 00:01:34.552
This is,

00:01:34.552 --> 00:01:37.263
a very sad morning in Israel.

00:01:37.263 --> 00:01:37.972
Very sad news

00:01:37.972 --> 00:01:40.725
coming out of the Gaza Strip. And,

00:01:40.725 --> 00:01:41.726
announcing today

00:01:41.726 --> 00:01:42.685
after we were able

00:01:42.685 --> 00:01:43.812
to talk to the families

00:01:43.812 --> 00:01:45.647
and inform them about

00:01:45.647 --> 00:01:48.108
finding the bodies of their loved ones.

00:01:48.108 --> 00:01:49.359
these were six people

00:01:49.359 --> 00:01:52.028
that were taken on October 7th, and,

00:01:52.028 --> 00:01:53.655
in our operations in Lofa,

00:01:54.697 --> 00:01:56.658
in an underground tunnel.

00:01:56.658 --> 00:01:57.700
We found their bodies,

00:01:57.700 --> 00:01:58.451
and we thought

00:01:58.451 --> 00:02:00.286
we brought them back to Israel.

00:02:00.286 --> 00:02:01.538
We examined them,

00:02:01.538 --> 00:02:03.373
and we found that they were,

00:02:03.373 --> 00:02:06.376
murdered by Hamas recently.

00:02:07.544 --> 00:02:10.088
and we were able to inform the families

00:02:10.088 --> 00:02:10.547
about it

00:02:10.547 --> 00:02:12.132
and share the news

00:02:12.132 --> 00:02:12.757
today, the very,

00:02:12.757 --> 00:02:14.342
very sad news about them.

00:02:14.342 --> 00:02:17.303
And and just to be clear, just because

00:02:17.303 --> 00:02:18.763
we're obviously,

00:02:18.763 --> 00:02:21.307
trying to get information about exactly

00:02:21.307 --> 00:02:25.770
how this this happened were, IDF soldiers

00:02:26.229 --> 00:02:30.275
actually looking for these six hostages,

00:02:30.275 --> 00:02:31.693
or did they find them

00:02:31.693 --> 00:02:34.237
as part of a separate,

00:02:34.237 --> 00:02:37.240
mission?

00:02:37.365 --> 00:02:38.158
But we

00:02:38.158 --> 00:02:39.659
we have been operating above

00:02:39.659 --> 00:02:40.827
and underground in that area,

00:02:40.827 --> 00:02:43.872
combating terrorists and, searching

00:02:43.872 --> 00:02:44.831
in the underground tunnels,

00:02:44.831 --> 00:02:47.250
as we've done in recent weeks in Lofa.

00:02:47.250 --> 00:02:50.253
And this is an area, I remind you, it's,

00:02:50.503 --> 00:02:51.296
less than a mile

00:02:51.296 --> 00:02:53.631
from where we found off on the,

00:02:53.631 --> 00:02:54.966
the hostage that we were able

00:02:54.966 --> 00:02:56.801
to rescue alive a few days ago.

00:02:56.801 --> 00:02:58.970
So there was some idea of hostages

00:02:58.970 --> 00:02:59.679
being in the area,

00:02:59.679 --> 00:03:01.890
but this was not a specific mission

00:03:01.890 --> 00:03:02.974
to release hostages.

00:03:02.974 --> 00:03:03.766
But,

00:03:03.766 --> 00:03:05.435
part of our ordinary,

00:03:05.435 --> 00:03:06.561
combat missions against

00:03:06.561 --> 00:03:07.896
Hamas above an underground.

00:03:09.939 --> 00:03:11.065
So you said that you

00:03:11.065 --> 00:03:14.068
believe that they were murdered recently?

00:03:15.069 --> 00:03:16.738
can you be more specific

00:03:16.738 --> 00:03:19.741
about how recently?

00:03:20.825 --> 00:03:22.493
Well, we are still, examining

00:03:22.493 --> 00:03:23.203
the information

00:03:23.203 --> 00:03:24.621
also operationally in the tunnel

00:03:24.621 --> 00:03:27.415
and also examining the bodies.

00:03:27.415 --> 00:03:28.374
and this is a process

00:03:28.374 --> 00:03:29.250
that might take a while,

00:03:29.250 --> 00:03:30.877
and we are personally obligated

00:03:30.877 --> 00:03:33.504
to inform the families.

00:03:33.504 --> 00:03:35.006
and then we'll have the information

00:03:35.006 --> 00:03:35.465
more public.

00:03:35.465 --> 00:03:38.259
But according to our initial,

00:03:38.259 --> 00:03:40.094
inquiry of the situation,

00:03:40.094 --> 00:03:41.554
they were murdered recently

00:03:41.554 --> 00:03:42.889
by Hamas terrorists.

00:03:42.889 --> 00:03:45.058
They were taken alive from Israel.

00:03:45.058 --> 00:03:47.185
They were, living in horrible conditions

00:03:47.185 --> 00:03:48.603
for almost a month.

00:03:48.603 --> 00:03:49.479
And recently,

00:03:49.479 --> 00:03:50.188
they were murdered

00:03:50.188 --> 00:03:52.982
by the terror organization.

00:03:52.982 --> 00:03:55.985
and we were able to find them, yesterday.

00:03:56.611 --> 00:03:58.321
do you have any idea?

00:03:58.321 --> 00:04:00.073
And I realize this is early

00:04:00.073 --> 00:04:01.241
and obviously,

00:04:01.241 --> 00:04:03.284
understandably, very delicate. Delicate.

00:04:03.284 --> 00:04:06.496
But do you have any idea, based on,

00:04:08.081 --> 00:04:09.666
when and where,

00:04:09.666 --> 00:04:11.251
these, individuals

00:04:11.251 --> 00:04:14.254
and their bodies were found that

00:04:15.380 --> 00:04:18.383
they were murdered.

00:04:18.466 --> 00:04:20.510
After hearing or sensing

00:04:20.510 --> 00:04:23.513
that the IDF was close by.

00:04:25.056 --> 00:04:26.182
Well, I

00:04:26.182 --> 00:04:27.141
we will be able to put

00:04:27.141 --> 00:04:27.976
that information later,

00:04:27.976 --> 00:04:29.686
but I think that that's not the question.

00:04:29.686 --> 00:04:31.771
Hamas is a terrorist organization

00:04:31.771 --> 00:04:33.022
that came to Israel,

00:04:33.022 --> 00:04:34.482
murdered thousands of people

00:04:34.482 --> 00:04:36.109
and abducted these

00:04:36.109 --> 00:04:36.943
innocent civilian

00:04:36.943 --> 00:04:39.112
young people from a party,

00:04:39.112 --> 00:04:40.446
and and they murdered them.

00:04:40.446 --> 00:04:41.281
And that is

00:04:41.281 --> 00:04:42.657
because they're a terrorist organization.

00:04:42.657 --> 00:04:43.783
And I think

00:04:43.783 --> 00:04:44.325
I would

00:04:44.325 --> 00:04:45.368
I would not be the one

00:04:45.368 --> 00:04:46.661
looking for reasons from us

00:04:46.661 --> 00:04:47.870
for why this this. No.

00:04:47.870 --> 00:04:48.871
The terror organization

00:04:48.871 --> 00:04:50.039
killing innocent civilians.

00:04:50.039 --> 00:04:53.042
One of them, an American civilian.

00:04:53.084 --> 00:04:53.876
you all know of

00:04:53.876 --> 00:04:55.920
that was was killed brutally. Yeah.

00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:57.213
I yeah.

00:04:57.213 --> 00:04:59.674
And I just want to make no mistake

00:04:59.674 --> 00:05:00.258
about this.

00:05:00.258 --> 00:05:02.385
Hamas is a terror organization,

00:05:02.385 --> 00:05:05.346
and they are the ones, to blame for this.

00:05:05.346 --> 00:05:06.472
I guess the reason I was

00:05:06.472 --> 00:05:08.099
asking that question is

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:10.476
whether or not

00:05:10.476 --> 00:05:12.395
they were close to being rescued.

00:05:12.395 --> 00:05:15.398
That was the basis for my question.

00:05:16.190 --> 00:05:16.482
Right.

00:05:16.482 --> 00:05:17.984
We're we're operating

00:05:17.984 --> 00:05:19.902
and we have a moral obligation

00:05:19.902 --> 00:05:21.863
and an operational priority

00:05:21.863 --> 00:05:24.157
to bring home their two 101 hostages.

00:05:24.157 --> 00:05:25.992
And we are working to bring them home

00:05:25.992 --> 00:05:28.244
as we have been able to bring,

00:05:28.244 --> 00:05:29.829
a few home one. Right.

00:05:29.829 --> 00:05:31.122
just last week.

00:05:31.122 --> 00:05:32.248
And we're operating for that

00:05:32.248 --> 00:05:33.916
and that that was part of our operation

00:05:33.916 --> 00:05:34.876
in that area.

00:05:34.876 --> 00:05:36.085
Hoping to find hostages.

00:05:36.085 --> 00:05:39.005
And sadly, we found them.

00:05:39.005 --> 00:05:39.922
we found bodies,

00:05:39.922 --> 00:05:41.716
but we're still operating in

00:05:41.716 --> 00:05:42.842
all parts of Gaza,

00:05:42.842 --> 00:05:44.260
hoping to find hostages.

00:05:44.260 --> 00:05:45.762
There are still many hostages alive.

00:05:45.762 --> 00:05:46.512
And that's why

00:05:46.512 --> 00:05:47.180
it's important for us

00:05:47.180 --> 00:05:48.973
to continue this pressure

00:05:48.973 --> 00:05:51.601
and to try and bring them home alive.

00:05:51.601 --> 00:05:53.436
Lieutenant Colonel Shoshana,

00:05:53.436 --> 00:05:54.937
thank you so much for being here.

00:05:54.937 --> 00:05:56.105
And again, we are

00:05:57.065 --> 00:05:58.066
just devastated

00:05:58.066 --> 00:06:01.069
by the news.

00:06:01.611 --> 00:06:04.280
Thank you.

