00:06:22.048 --> 00:06:24.550
this morning.

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:28.096
particularly given the fact that I know

00:06:28.096 --> 00:06:29.222
how close you are

00:06:29.222 --> 00:06:30.723
to all of the hostage families,

00:06:30.723 --> 00:06:32.350
but particularly,

00:06:32.350 --> 00:06:35.561
the the Goldberg pollens, the two.

00:06:35.561 --> 00:06:38.314
Hirsh and Omar, almost the same age.

00:06:38.314 --> 00:06:40.400
Omar is

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.860
going to turn 23 next month,

00:06:42.860 --> 00:06:44.529
and I can't imagine how difficult

00:06:44.529 --> 00:06:45.988
it must be

00:06:45.988 --> 00:06:49.117
to watch this news, knowing that

00:06:49.367 --> 00:06:52.370
your beautiful son is still in captivity.

00:06:54.997 --> 00:06:56.416
It's absolutely right, Dana.

00:06:56.416 --> 00:06:58.042
There are no words for us, really,

00:06:58.042 --> 00:07:00.670
to comfort all the families.

